SUMMARY:R.E.M. + The Replacements tribute bands
DESCRIPTION:Two of indie rock’s most influential bands come to life for one night only. The Ones You Love channel the jangly urgency and anthemic sweep of R.E.M.\, while Ashtray Floors bring the raw\, ragged spirit of The Replacements. Expect a set packed with college rock classics\, deep cuts\, and sing-along favorites—equal parts nostalgia and high-energy live show. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
