SUMMARY:JAAK live at Montclair Brewery
DESCRIPTION:JAAK is an original jazz fusion band located in Hudson County\, NJ. Consisting of trumpet\, sax\,keys\, bass\, and drums\, their sound crosses different styles including jazz\, funk\, R&B\, hip hop\,pop\, rock\, and video game music. JAAK has two singles out on streaming platforms\, with an EPand more original music on the way. JAAK has played in venues and events around HudsonCounty\, including Brightside Tavern\, Hendrickson’s Corner\, Groove on Grove Festival\, WPUBraveathon Radio Show\, and Green Space Studios. JAAK also covers various artists\, andinspires their sound from the likes of Miles Davis\, Freddie Hubbard\, Billy Cobham\, Billy Ocean\,Tony Williams\, and Steely Dan. \n$5 cover charge per person that goes directly to the artists. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
