SUMMARY:Reiki Infused Sound Bath & Chakra Balancing with Vinni
DESCRIPTION:New Moon in Aries Sound Bath\, Chakra Balancing & Reiki \nYou’ll be guided through a chakra-balancing journey supported by healing sounds from Himalayan singing bowls and gong\, while receiving Reiki energy to gently clear emotional and energetic blockages. There will also be an opportunity to stand within a large sound bowl\, allowing the vibrations to move through the body and nervous system\, supporting deep grounding\, rooting\, and energetic stabilization. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
